item.description: I am a third-year Ph.D. student in Statistics at Monash University, supervised by Rob J Hyndman and Anastasios Panagiotelis. My research interests include manifold learning, time series analysis, and statistical computing. I am currently working on a project about Manifold learning on empirical probability distributions.
